main event: Several round objects were observed at a great height in the sky in Edmonton, Alberta, Canada on June 29, 1959.
interesting points: Objects were approximately the size of a basketball and white in color., Objects appeared and disappeared at irregular intervals., The objects moved in a horizontal direction at very high speed., No sound was audible during the sighting., The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes.
sighted object: several round white objects in the sky
witness description: Ground visual observation without clearly identified witnesses.
